o be confident and happy in myself as an athlete and as a person and you are seeing that.\", \"from\": 3419, \"to\": 3571, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The Olympic silver medallist, aged 23, dominated the heats|GETTYHunt, who won World Championship silver in the women's 200m in Tokyo last September, insists her confidence has risen despite defeat.She added: \\\"Obviously, it not nice to lose to one of your biggest rivals, so I am slightly frustrated.\", \"from\": 3571, \"to\": 3871, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3699, \"end\": 3704, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9991659764289829, \"rank\": 0.0008347153600164037, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But on the plus side we are getting a lot more consistent.\", \"from\": 3872, \"to\": 3930, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The medals made me into a more confident runner and person.\", \"from\": 3930, \"to\": 3990, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am super excited for outdoors.\", \"from\": 3991, \"to\": 4023, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Jeremiah Azu retained his British indoor title with victory in the men's 60m final, coming home in 6.56 seconds with Romell Glave runner-up in 6.62secs and will aim to defend the world indoor title he won last year in Poland next month.Our Standards:The GB News Editorial Charter  Her performance ranks as the quickest 800m run anywhere in the world for nearly a quarter of a century, placing her third on the all-time list for the distance.\", \"from\": 4023, \"to\": 4465, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4024, \"end\": 4036, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeremiah_Azu\", \"score\": 0.9999990537371489, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jeremiah Azu\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeremiah_Azu\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeremiah_Azu\"}, {\"begi