s and pick what I am able to do and have nothing holding me back.\\\"\", \"from\": 6204, \"to\": 6309, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Keely Hodgkinson smashed her own British indoor 800m record at the UK Indoor Championships in Birmingham  GETTY  Elsewhere, Dina Asher-Smith took the women's 60m crown in 7.05, ahead of World Championship silver medallist Amy Hunt who finished second.\", \"from\": 6311, \"to\": 6562, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6311, \"end\": 6327, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Keely Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\"}, {\"begin\": 6344, \"end\": 6351, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"score\": 0.9918967851014996, \"rank\": 0.004989357484792364, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\"}, {\"begin\": 6378, \"end\": 6380, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.997146355001412, \"rank\": 0.0028617365170360504, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 6405, \"end\": 6415, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Birmingham_City_F.C.\", \"score\": 0.9935998665845149, \"rank\": 0.00644135897118202, \"text\": \"Birmingham\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Birmingham_City_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Birmingham_City_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 6435, \"end\": 6451, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dina_Asher-Smith\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Dina Asher-Smith\", \"types\": 